<dl id="n19037g"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n19" href="#n19037g">N19 (VI.B.19)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n19all.htm#n19037g"> 37(g)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> scoptophilia</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">The pleasure which a person takes in his own sexual organ may become associated with <mark>scoptophilia</mark> (or sexual pleasure in looking) in its active and passive forms, in a manner which has been very aptly described by Alfred Adler as &lsquo;confluence of instincts&rsquo;k. <small> Sigmund Freud, <a name="SFLH" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#SFLH"><cite title="source">&ldquo;Analysis of a Phobia in a Five-Year old boy&rdquo; (&lsquo;Little Hans&rsquo;)&rdquo;</cite></a> (May 1925) 248</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
